    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Toshinori Munakata</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:134px;\"><a href=\"http://cis.csuohio.edu/~munakata/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/2/27/ToshinoriMunakata.jpg\" width=\"132\" height=\"156\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:ToshinoriMunakata.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Toshinori Munakata <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Toshinori Munakata</b>,<br />\na <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Japanese_Americans\">Japanese American</a> computer scientist, \nand distinguished professor emeritus at Computer and Information Science Department, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cleveland_State_University\">Cleveland State University</a>, \nholding a B.Sc., M.Sc. and Ph.D. from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Tokyo\">University of Tokyo</a>. \nHis research interests include <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">artificial intelligence</a>, new <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Programming_paradigm\">computing paradigms</a>, and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Analysis_of_algorithms\">analysis</a> of <a href=\"/Algorithms\" title=\"Algorithms\">algorithms</a> \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \nSince coming to the US in 1967, Toshinori Munakata research has spanned many of AI's most important realms, <a href=\"/Neural_Networks\" title=\"Neural Networks\">neural networks</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fuzzy_logic\">fuzzy logic</a>, <a href=\"/Genetic_Programming#EvolutionaryComputation\" title=\"Genetic Programming\">evolutionary computing</a>, and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chaos_theory\">chaotic systems</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1979_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1979 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#1990_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1990 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2010\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Toshinori_Munakata&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1979_...\">1979 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Toshinori_Munakata&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1979 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Toshinori Munakata</a> (<b>1979</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/Matrices-and-linear-programming-with-applications-Munakata/207231dba7d137926f6d536120a81154dcb2022b\">Matrices and Linear Programming with Applications</a></i>. Holden-Day, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Matrices-programming-applications-Toshinori-Munakata/dp/0816261660\">amazon.com</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Toshinori Munakata</a> (<b>1985</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0020737385800584\">Knowledge-Based Systems for Genetics</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.journals.elsevier.com/international-journal-of-human-computer-studies\">International Journal of Man-Machine Studies</a>, Vol. 23, No. 5</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/y/Yeh:D=_Yun\">D. Yun Yeh</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Toshinori Munakata</a> (<b>1986</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/doi/10.1145/5657.5662\">Dynamic Initial Allocation and Local Reallocation Procedures for Multiple Stacks</a></i>. <a href=\"/ACM#Communications\" title=\"ACM\">Communications of the ACM</a>, Vol. 29, No. 2</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1990_...\">1990 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Toshinori_Munakata&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 1990 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Toshinori Munakata</a> (<b>1992</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/doi/10.1145/131295.131300\">Notes on Implementing Sets in Prolog</a></i>. <a href=\"/ACM#Communications\" title=\"ACM\">Communications of the ACM</a>, Vol. 35, No. 3</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Toshinori Munakata</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/j/Jani:Yashvant\">Yashvant Jani</a> (<b>1994</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/doi/10.1145/175247.175254\">Fuzzy Systems: An Overview</a></i>. <a href=\"/ACM#Communications\" title=\"ACM\">Communications of the ACM</a>, Vol. 37, No. 3</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Toshinori Munakata</a> (<b>1995</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/doi/abs/10.1145/219717.219734\">New Horizons in Commercial and Industrial AI</a></i>. <a href=\"/ACM#Communications\" title=\"ACM\">Communications of the ACM</a>, Vol. 38, No. 11</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=9c96P6cAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">William L. Ditto</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Toshinori Munakata</a> (<b>1995</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/doi/10.1145/219717.219797\">Principles and Applications of Chaotic Systems</a></i>. <a href=\"/ACM#Communications\" title=\"ACM\">Communications of the ACM</a>, Vol. 38, No. 11, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/download?doi=10.1.1.120.2481&amp;rep=rep1&amp;type=pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Toshinori Munakata</a> (<b>1996</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/doi/10.1145/233977.234001\">Thoughts on Deep Blue vs. Kasparov</a></i>. <a href=\"/ACM#Communications\" title=\"ACM\">Communications of the ACM</a>, Vol. 39, No. 7, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://cis.csuohio.edu/~munakata/publs/pdf/cacm96.pdf\">pdf</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Kasparov_versus_Deep_Blue_1996\" title=\"Kasparov versus Deep Blue 1996\">Kasparov versus Deep Blue 1996</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yasser_Seirawan\">Yasser Seirawan</a>, <a href=\"/Herbert_Simon\" title=\"Herbert Simon\">Herbert Simon</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Toshinori Munakata</a> (<b>1997</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/doi/10.1145/257874.257878\">The Implications of Kasparov vs. Deep Blue</a></i>. <a href=\"/ACM#Communications\" title=\"ACM\">Communications of the ACM</a>, Vol. 40, No. 8, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://archive.computerhistory.org/projects/chess/related_materials/text/5-4.The_implications_of_deep_blue_vs_kasparov/5-4.The_implications_of_deep_blue_vs_kasparov.simon_seirawan.1997.ACM.062303057.sm.pdf\">pdf</a> hosted by <a href=\"/The_Computer_History_Museum\" title=\"The Computer History Museum\">The Computer History Museum</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Kasparov_versus_Deep_Blue_1997\" title=\"Kasparov versus Deep Blue 1997\">Kasparov versus Deep Blue 1997</a></li>\n<li> <span id=\"FundamentalsNAI1st\"></span><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Toshinori Munakata</a> (<b>1998</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://cis.csuohio.edu/~munakata/publs/book/sp.html\">Fundamentals of the New Artificial Intelligence: Beyond Traditional Paradigms</a></i>. 1st edition, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Springer_Science%2BBusiness_Media\">Springer</a>, <a href=\"/Toshinori_Munakata#FundamentalsNAI2nd\" title=\"Toshinori Munakata\">2nd edition 2008</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Toshinori Munakata</a> (<b>1998</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0165011496003892\">Notes on implementing fuzzy sets in Prolog</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fuzzy_Sets_and_Systems\">Fuzzy Sets and Systems</a>, Vol. 98, No. 3</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Toshinori Munakata</a> (<b>1999</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/doi/10.1145/319382.319387\">Knowledge Discovery - Introduction</a></i>. <a href=\"/ACM#Communications\" title=\"ACM\">Communications of the ACM</a>, Vol. 42, No. 11</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Toshinori_Munakata&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/m/Mak:Brenda.html\">Brenda Mak</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Toshinori Munakata</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ideas.repec.org/a/eee/ejores/v136y2002i1p212-229.html\">Rule extraction from expert heuristics: A comparative study of rough sets with neural networks and ID3</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/European_Journal_of_Operational_Research\">European Journal of Operational Research</a>, Vol. 136, No. 1 <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Toshinori Munakata</a> (<b>2007</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-71200-8_14\">A Personal View on AI, Rough Set Theory and Professor Pawlak</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/book/10.1007/978-3-540-71200-8\">Transactions on Rough Sets VI</a>  <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <span id=\"FundamentalsNAI2nd\"></span><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Toshinori Munakata</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/book/10.1007/978-1-84628-839-5\">Fundamentals of the New Artificial Intelligence: Neural, Evolutionary, Fuzzy and More</a></i>. 2nd edition, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Springer_Science%2BBusiness_Media\">Springer</a>, <a href=\"/Toshinori_Munakata#FundamentalsNAI1st\" title=\"Toshinori Munakata\">1st edition 1998</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010\">2010</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Toshinori_Munakata&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2010\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Toshinori Munakata</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/t/Takahashi:Jun\">Jun Takahashi</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=jWUz2vcAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Munehisa Sekikawa</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/a/Aihara:Kazuyuki.html\">Kazuyuki Aihara</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/17445760902774898\">Chaos computing: a unified view</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.tandfonline.com/toc/gpaa20/current\">International Journal of Parallel, Emergent and Distributed Systems</a>, Vol. 25, No. 1</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=qBceGegAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Masashi Aono</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/k/Kim:Song=Ju\">Song-Ju Kim</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/h/Hara:Masahiko\">Masahiko Hara</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Toshinori Munakata</a> (<b>2014</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24384066/\">Amoeba-inspired Tug-of-War algorithms for exploration-exploitation dilemma in extended Bandit Problem</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.journals.elsevier.com/biosystems/\">Biosystems</a> 117, 1-9, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://cis.csuohio.edu/~munakata/publs/pdf/BioSystems14.pdf\">pdf</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Toshinori_Munakata&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://cis.csuohio.edu/~munakata/\">Munakata's Home Page</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Toshinori_Munakata&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Image (cropped) from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://cis.csuohio.edu/~munakata/\">Munakata's Home Page</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://cis.csuohio.edu/~munakata/profess/profess.htm\">Munakata's Home Page - Professional Information</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/m/Munakata:Toshinori\">dblp: Toshinori Munakata</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rough_set\">Rough set from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ID3_algorithm\">ID3 algorithm from Wikipedia</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Ross_Quinlan\" title=\"Ross Quinlan\">Ross Quinlan</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Mathematician#ZPawlak\" title=\"Mathematician\">Mathematician | Zdzisław Pawlak</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Physarum_polycephalum\">Physarum polycephalum from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tug_of_war\">Tug of war from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Multi-armed_bandit\">Multi-armed bandit from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301031426\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.028 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.029 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 159/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 342/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:7265-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301031426 and revision id 19921\n -->\n"
